E4Plus1.uk.description: The Intimacy Acceleration: When the gang hear about an experiment designed to make participants fall in love, Sheldon and Penny put it to the test as a joke. (S8 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Slight at the Opera: Cameron is putting on the school production of Phantom of the Opera, but when their star falls ill, Manny pulls out all the stops to land the lead. (S4 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bad Hair Day: Claire flies solo to her college reunion, where she bumps into a professor who she once dated, and when Phil shows up things get awkward. (S4 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Sibling Realignment: When Sheldon finds out that his mum won't come to his wedding unless he invites his brother Georgie, he and Leonard head to Texas. (S11 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bow Tie Asymmetry: Everyone is focused on making sure that the arrangements for Amy and Sheldon's big day go according to plan - except the bride and groom. (S11 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conjugal Configuration: Sheldon and Amy's honeymoon runs aground, while Penny and Leonard discover that they are uncomfortably similar to Amy's parents. (S12 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wedding Gift Wormhole: A stressed Sheldon and Amy struggle to work out what the 'perfect gift' is that Leonard and Penny gave them on their wedding day. (S12 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Lake House: The squad take Captain Holt up on an offer of a weekend getaway. (S8 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Blue Flu: Captain Holt and Amy manage an understaffed precinct while Jake and Charles investigate why so many cops have been taken ill there at the same time. (S8 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Manger Things: A secret from Flanders' past is revealed, and we discover a room in the Simpsons' home that we've never seen before. (S32 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Uncut Femmes: It turns out that there's more to Chief Wiggum's wife than it seems. And Marge gets involved in a jewel heist. (S32 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: As Homestays continue, an emotional mum expresses unease, and friend feedback falls flat. And how will one bride cope with her family's commitment concerns? (S10 Ep28)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Decision Reverberation: Raj publishes a paper that suggests he may have discovered alien life. Penny encourages Leonard to stand up for himself. (S12 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Crook and Ladder: When members of the Springfield fire department are injured, Homer, Moe, Apu and Skinner volunteer to be temporary firefighters. (S18 Ep19/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stop or My Dog Will Shoot: After rescuing Homer from a corn maze, Santa's Little Helper is recruited as a police dog and is teamed up with grizzled veteran cop Lou. (S18 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: The villagers unite in grief as they say goodbye to Peri. Donny faces turmoil after his worlds collide, and families try to rebuild, but will life in Hollyoaks ever be the same again?

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: MAFS UK Does Come Dine...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...with Me: Brand new series - Kieran Chapman hopes to tickle his guests' fancy with a clown-themed carnival of delights. But is serving dessert with chopsticks a joke too far? (Ep2/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Diane von Furstenberg: Iconic reality with Tyra Banks. The 14 models hit the runway - four storeys in the air! And a swimsuit shoot focuses on teen bullying. (S15 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At the final Commitment Ceremony, one bride faces up to some difficult truths, and the revelation of a scandal sends shockwaves through the group. (S10 Ep29)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Visual glazing enhancer (window cleaner) Daniel bonds with Margot Robbie lookalike Lora over nostril waxing and raving, but is he over his ex? Fireman Mark fans Ellie's flame. (S7 Ep16/17)

Film4.uk.description: (2022) Creepy-doll horror with Allison Williams. A robotics engineer simultaneously invents an AI dolly and takes on the care of her orphaned niece. But can a cyborg really raise a kid?

Film4.uk.description: (2021) Tom Hardy returns as Marvel's gnarly antihero, to face a symbiote spawned from Venom's own blood living inside a serial killer who looks just like Woody Harrelson. Yikes.

Film4.uk.title: First Knight
Film4.uk.description: (1995) Romantic drama based on Arthurian legend, starring Richard Gere, Sean Connery and Julia Ormond. Can nomadic swordsman Lancelot contain his love for King Arthur's fiance?

Film4.uk.title: Transformers: Revenge of the...

Film4.uk.title: One Day
Film4.uk.description: (2011) Romantic drama. Jim Sturgess and Anne Hathaway star as friends whose lives intertwine and diverge over the years, after first meeting as graduates in 1988.

Film4.uk.title: Deadpool 2
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Ryan Reynolds returns as the potty-mouthed, can of whup-ass-opening superhero and now he's got buddies to help him take on baddie Josh Brolin in the all-out action comedy sequel.

Film4.uk.title: Good Boys
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Coming-of-age comedy about three young boys embarking on a brand new, terrifying adventure: sixth grade. Girls, kissing and an epic four-mile journey await.

Film4.uk.title: Moneyboys
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Gritty drama set in South China following the life of a male sex worker who must juggle the demands of his family, while keeping how he supports them a secret. In Mandarin/subs.

Film4.uk.title: Mandy

Film4.uk.title: Rio Grande
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Western. John Wayne plays the commander of a Texan fort at which his ex-wife (Maureen O'Hara) pitches up. Can he win back her love by saving kidnapped children from Apache raiders?

Film4.uk.title: Father Brown
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Crime-comedy starring Alec Guinness. A priest is tasked with accompanying a priceless religious artifact from London to Rome. But the prolific thief Flambeau is hot on his trail...

Film4.uk.title: The Colditz Story
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Classic Second World War drama. John Mills, Lionel Jeffries and Bryan Forbes star as just some of the POWs determined to break out of the infamous German 'escape-proof' prison.

Film4.uk.title: Starman
Film4.uk.description: (1984) John Carpenter's sci-fi romance with Jeff Bridges and Karen Allen. An alien is stranded on Earth, where he assumes the form of a widow's dead husband - and finds the locals hostile.

Film4.uk.title: Where the Crawdads Sing
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Daisy Edgar-Jones stars in director Olivia Newman's adaptation of Delia Owens' best-selling novel about a feral child who's accused of murder in America's Deep South. Did she do it?

Film4.uk.title: How I Live Now
Film4.uk.description: (2012) Saoirse Ronan and George MacKay star in director Kevin Macdonald's romance-thriller about a US teen who falls in love just as Europe tips into war. Very strong language.

Film4.uk.title: The Nevadan
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Western with Randolph Scott and Dorothy Malone. A cunning US Marshal pretends to be a doofus to get a bank robber to take him to the hidden loot.

Film4.uk.title: The Bravados
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Brooding western starring Joan Collins and Gregory Peck. A man hunts down the four escaped prisoners who he believes are responsible for the murder of his wife.

Film4.uk.title: The Winslow Boy
Film4.uk.description: (1948) Anthony Asquith's drama based on a famous 1912 court case with Cedric Hardwicke as the father of a boy accused of theft who pursues the case to the highest courts. With Robert Donat.

Film4.uk.description: (2021) Action thriller with Gerard Butler. A hitman gets himself arrested so that he can get to a bad guy, who also got himself arrested, so that he could hide from the hitman.

Film4.uk.title: Late Night with the Devil
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Unsettling found-footage horror with David Dastmalchian. A has-been host tries to save his 70s talk show using a demonically possessed 13-year-old girl. Really, what could go wrong?
